OL,3,CCornish holiday park owner feels
OL,4,C'victimised' by government tax changes
OL,6,FHe said: "We have about 30 employees
OL,7,Fhere at the moment, which we keep on
OL,8,Fall year round. Due to some of the tax
OL,9,Fchanges, I now would look very
OL,10,Fcarefully at replacing any employee
OL,11,Fthat left.
OL,13,F"Similarly, I'm looking at whether to
OL,14,Freplace any caravans. Normally I buy
OL,15,Fnew caravans every year, that may not
OL,16,Fbe possible now.
