OL,3,CCornish holiday park owner feels
OL,4,C'victimised' by government tax changes
OL,6,F"We've got to look at retaining money
OL,7,Fin the business or taking out perhaps
OL,8,Finsurance policies, spending money on
OL,9,Flegal and accountancy advice, which,
OL,10,Ffrankly, we just see is dead money.
OL,12,F"It's all about looking how to protect
OL,13,Fthe business from what we see as a tax
OL,14,Fgrab. I feel victimised by this
OL,15,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
