OL,3,CCornish holiday park owner feels
OL,4,C'victimised' by government tax changes
OL,6,F"It's almost as though we're the enemy
OL,7,Fand they don't want family businesses
OL,8,Fto thrive. And I know we want to fund
OL,9,Fthe NHS and all the other things
OL,10,Fgovernment has to do, but they also
OL,11,Fhave to take into account there is an
OL,12,Funintended consequence".
OL,14,FAndrew still hopes to pass the family
OL,15,Frun holiday park on to his daughter
OL,16,Fwho is involved in the business but is
OL,17,Fconsidering all options.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
