OL,3,CCornish holiday park owner feels
OL,4,C'victimised' by government tax changes
OL,6,F"The impact of the business property
OL,7,Frelief and inheritance tax changes is
OL,8,Fquite massive. Potentially it could
OL,9,Fput a #1 million tax bill on the
OL,10,Fbusiness. One exit would be to sell
OL,11,Fthe whole business, but quite likely
OL,12,Fit could be bought by one of the big
OL,13,Fgroups.
OL,15,F"I think it's a shame because you then
OL,16,Flose out on the personal attention and
OL,17,Fthe detail on the park and the care
OL,18,Fyou get from being family-owned rather
OL,19,Fthan being part of a group".
