OL,3,CCornish holiday park owner feels
OL,4,C'victimised' by government tax changes
OL,6,FA new report from Family Business UK
OL,7,Fand CBI Economics reveals that family-
OL,8,Fowned businesses in the South West are
OL,9,Fexpecting to cut almost 19,000 jobs
OL,10,Fand reduce investment by more than 16%
OL,11,Fleading to a drop in economic activity
OL,12,Fworth almost #1.3bn.
OL,14,FDeborah Walker, Director General of
OL,15,Fthe British Holidays and Home Parks
OL,16,FAssociation wants the government to
OL,17,Freverse its decision. She said" "We're
OL,18,Furging the government to take another
OL,19,Flook at the figures. The government
OL,20,Fthinks that it's going to raise taxes
OL,21,Fwith this inheritance tax.
