OL,3,CCornish holiday park owner feels
OL,4,C'victimised' by government tax changes
OL,6,F"But the figures show that there
OL,7,Factually is actually going to cost the
OL,8,FTreasury #130 million and what it's
OL,9,Falso going to do is force much loved
OL,10,Ffamily-run businesses to have to sell
OL,11,Fup or close down and those are exactly
OL,12,Fthe sort of businesses that are
OL,13,Fdriving rural and coastal economies."
OL,15,FThe new rules on Business Property
OL,16,FRelief are set to come into effect in
OL,17,FApril 2026.
