OL,6,FIn response a HM Treasury spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our reforms to Agricultural and
OL,8,FBusiness Property Reliefs will mean
OL,9,Fthree quarters of estates will
OL,10,Fcontinue to pay no inheritance tax at
OL,11,Fall, while the remaining quarter will
OL,12,Fpay half the inheritance tax that most
OL,13,Festates pay, and payments can be
OL,14,Fspread over 10 years, interest-free.
OL,15,FThis is a fair and balanced approach
OL,16,Fwhich helps fix the public services we
OL,17,Fall rely on.
